## Cron task creation

When creating a new cron, every script MUST include:
```bash
CRON_MODEL="${CRON_MODEL:-}"
# later:
MODEL_FLAG=""
if [[ -n "$CRON_MODEL" ]]; then
  MODEL_FLAG="--model $CRON_MODEL"
fi
OUT=$(claude -p "$PROMPT" \
  --output-format text \
  --permission-mode acceptEdits \
  $MODEL_FLAG \
  --allowed-tools "Bash,Read,Write,Edit,WebFetch,Glob,Grep" \
  --thinking enabled \
  2>&1) || true
```

